description: Lists the results of the Security Hub insight specified by the insight ARN.

parameters.name: InsightArn
parameters.description: The ARN of the insight for which to return results.

nested_items.name: InsightResults
nested_items.description: The insight results returned by the operation.

nested_items.name: InsightArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the insight whose results are returned by the GetInsightResults operation.

nested_items.name: GroupByAttribute
nested_items.description: The attribute that the findings are grouped by for the insight whose results are returned by the GetInsightResults operation.

nested_items.name: ResultValues
nested_items.description: The list of insight result values returned by the GetInsightResults operation.

nested_items.name: GroupByAttributeValue
nested_items.description: The value of the attribute that the findings are grouped by for the insight whose results are returned by the GetInsightResults operation.

nested_items.name: Count
nested_items.description: The number of findings returned for each GroupByAttributeValue.
